author_ssm: Rob Fellman, Phil Lauer, and Marvin Taylor
unittitle_ssm: Ralph E. Pickett Papers
abstract_ssm: Ralph Pickett was a professor at NYU at the School of Education, donor to the Library, and the author of numerous works of fiction, most of which remain unpublished. The papers are primarily typewritten manuscripts of Pickett's unpublished fiction.
corpname_ssm: New York University. School of Education
